{
  "stem": "3341.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If they would have found out that I am in the flat, they would have called the police, or maybe burglar is there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So you can imagine I was really quiet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in '44. '44.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the other episode of my life, which-- in 1943-- from '43 to '44, they were nonstop deporting Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were living in and out, in and out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From '42 and '43, I came home when it was convenient.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was living illegally.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We, we were taking such risks which we didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day in 1943, it could have been in March or April, I had a naive idea, which I didn't even say to my parents.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I, I wrote a letter to the Ministry of Education, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, I am a graduate of textile academy, which was very well known in peaceful time, and I can call it peaceful time, in Brno.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in Slovakia, they had a small textile industry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One of the big factories-- the biggest actually-- was in the town where I was in the military hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That is called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a big factory, 1,500, maybe 2,000 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that is, for Slovakian conditions, big.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I wrote to the ministry of education saying, because Slovakia has not a textile academy, which would be very useful for the industry which is now-- because during the war, anything which was produced in manufacturing way was booming.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had shortage of textiles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anything they could produce-- ordinary cotton for bed sheets or something-- not complicated products, they couldn't make enough.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, I explained that, in the letter, that I would establish, with a friend of mine-- who was also a graduate of, of textile.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went to the same class with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
